---
title: Za'atar and Feta Flatbread with Spinach Salad and Sliced Almonds
description: There's nothing like a free-form flatbread to make you feel a bit fancy at dinnertime. This colourful beauty is all about the tender zucchini, the sweetness of cooked shallots and the salty finish of feta. It's unbeatable!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/zaatar-and-feta-flatbread-50c707d9.jpg
